{"tid":2213182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教協民調: 多數會員撐議員留任一年","createTime":"2020-09-22T10:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T14:25:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd38789a6c38f418ed4b6a8297f8d0c137fc6fe","tid":2213182,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"(<strong>呢個係教協民調, 唔係香港民意研究所進行去留民調. &nbsp;</strong>)<br />\n<br />\n我早公開預計: 大部分飯民議員都會走, 剩下部分最保守兼食古不化既議員入臨立會.<br />\n所以今次教協民調, 都係預撚左.. &nbsp;葉建聯準備入臨立會. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>逾10位民主派委託香港民意研究所進行「去留民調」，表明會服從民調結果，決定係咪接受延任一年，民調結果料下周三（30日）公佈。其餘民主派議員中，部份會睇吓業界意見，其中教育界已完成收集教協會員意見，結果多數會員支持留任，教協未有最終決定，但呢個會員民調結果係最主要考慮因素。</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/YJJ3AACAJJHWJHHB3AA6HCACCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2FYJJ3AACAJJHWJHHB3AA6HCACCQ%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=6c58078f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2FYJJ3AACAJJHWJHHB3AA6HCACCQ%2F&h=ba39b0ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/YJJ3AACAJJHWJHHB3AA6HCACCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"a0411cf51ed5cc29cfb301a81608ca86d5dc5284","tid":2213182,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:45:32.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰, 鄺俊宇都準備杯葛了,<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2212606/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2212606/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2195689/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2195689/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"aa85518a83a643482684a40dd4f08892c6f16527","tid":2213182,"uid":108347,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:48:29.000Z","msg":"係咪唔知咩叫功能組別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢就係唔使對市民負責"},{"p